hello_neo4j.description:
Get some statistics out of your Neo4j instance.
Call hello_neo4j --help to see the usage.

cypher.description:
Use Neo4j's Cypher shell to execute Cypher queries.
Interactive shell without parameters or e.g. jbang cypher -a neo4j://localhost:7687 -u neo4j -p secret 'MATCH (n) return n'
